<h2><span class="editsection">[<a href="../../w/index-title=Queluz_National_Palace&action=edit&section=1.php.html" title="Edit section: Architecture and history">edit</a>]</span> <span class="mw-headline" id="Architecture_and_history">Architecture and history</span></h2>
<div class="thumb tleft">
<div class="thumbinner" style="width:302px;">
<div class="noresize"><map name="ImageMap_2_751008808" id="ImageMap_2_751008808">
